<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 480px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
      }
      .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #6c47ff;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .text {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #555555;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .otp-box {
        background: #f0ecff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .otp-code {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #6c47ff;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
      }
      .expires {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #999999;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #aaaaaa;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 32px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">🔥 {{appName}}</div>
      <div class="title">Tasdiqlash kodi</div>
      <p class="text">
        Salom! Quyidagi kodni ishlatib emailingizni tasdiqlang:
      </p>
      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <div class="expires">Kod {{expiresIn}} ichida amal qiladi</div>
      </div>
      <p class="text">
        Agar siz bu so'rovni yubormagan bo'lsangiz, ushbu xabarni e'tiborsiz qoldiring.
      </p>
      <div class="footer">© 2025 {{appName}}. Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan.</div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>